description: A man thought to be in his 60s dies and five more are injured while working on a site in Tralee.
title: Kerry: Man dies after part of a building collapses in Tralee
title_page: Kerry: Man dies after part of a building collapses in Tralee - BBC News
maintext: A man has died and five other men have been injured after part of a building collapsed in County Kerry in the Republic of Ireland.
